            </opener>
            <p>Just another line to you my dear old friend to send you my best love
                &#38; my warmest sympathy<ptr target="loc.02538_n4"/></p>
            <p>God bless you &#38; keep you &#38; make his face to shine upon you 
                &#38; give you peace&#8212;perfect <hi rend="underline">peace</hi>&#8212;His Peace! 
                is the prayer of
            </p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Yours affectionately</salute>
                <signed><hi rend="underline">J Johnston</hi></signed> 
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02546.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
